headline: Wolfe Research Upgrades The Williams Companies (WMB) Stock
summary: The Williams Companies, Inc. (NYSE:WMB) is one of the Top Energy and Utility Stocks Wall Street Analysts Are Talking About. headline: Buy Kinder Morgan Stock. Natural Gas and AI Are a Potent Combination.
summary: Steady demand for natural gas and supply bottlenecks have helped pipeline operators like Kinder Morgan.  The stock is also a way to play artificial intelligence’s energy appetite.  Pipeline projects should proliferate in the current U.S. political climate.
